 spirit, the bond between mothers and their child, and the power of dreaming beyond hope.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI give it my strongest, highest recommendation and know it will be a runaway bestseller!","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/39752697?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1185213123"},"likeCount":4,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:39727633":{"id":39727633,"__typename":"User","legacyId":39727633,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1422578888i/39727633.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1,"viewableName":"Courtney Garner","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/39727633-courtney-garner","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":0},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.Pf2qOxd2JQ-3hRUb3Mfjmg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.Pf2qOxd2JQ-3hRUb3Mfjmg","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.8vmA3k5eQ76SSWNjAqYVoQ"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:39727633"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1472608655489,"createdAt":1422578889000,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1422721827000,"text":"I just finished reading this book and it is very powerful. At first I was struck by the fair-haired heroine, Ellen, and how strong and self-sacrificing she was. But when I came to the end of the book, my opinion completely changed about Hee Ae. She was a heroine also. She made the ultimate sacrifice for her son - she gave him up for a better, richer life. I cried for Young Nam and felt so proud of Noah. Beautifully written. The images stay with you long after you finish the story. ","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","w